data.description: Tastefully renovated 3 bedroom 2 bath with large backyard. Spacious living and dining area with WBFP. Beautifully update kitchen including new custom cabinets, granite and stainless appliances. Both baths have been fully updated. Some of the other updates include new windows, ceiling fans, light fixtures, doors, interior exterior paint and flooring. Great starter home in a beautiful neighborhood with the city park across the street. Great school district.
